468502,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb9ed1938b1c12eabc3090d33b2aaff48933cc6","tid":1468502,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:10:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f281278269ad376650d7a8b2b449cca26285090","tid":1468502,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:15:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fc532170636300908df91f123205383d013cbed","tid":1468502,"uid":296055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:20:46.000Z","msg":"各位請幫忙分享出去！！！如果你們願意，請幫忙分享以下道歉文章到自己的Facebook,ig,爭取在林鄭講廢話指責我地之前，為811及812中在場記者，救護人員，機場職員及旅客等受影響人士致歉而道歉。並請繼續分享出去！！！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n鑒於這兩天於機場舉行的和平理性機場集會，為各位旅客帶不便，在此，我們真心誠意向各位致歉。<br />\n<br />\nWe would like to sincerely apologize for all the inconvenience caused by the peaceful demonstration at the HK International Airport over the last two days.<br />\n<br />\n我們重申，今次的機場集會，目的為和平理性地引起政府回應及國際關注，希望各位能夠體諒，香港人爭取五大訴求嘅初衷。<br />\n<br />\nOur demonstration aims to peacefully raise the awareness of the global community, as well as response from the HK government on the five demands from the public of Hong Kong. We thank you for your tolerance and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n我們再次向在場記者，救護人員，機場職員及旅客等受影響人士致歉，感謝各位的諒解。<br />\n<br />\nTo all the reporters, ambulance staff, airport staff and affected passengers, we again would like to express oir deepest apology to all the inconvenience and disruptions<br />\n<br />\n感謝所有仍堅持初心嘅香港人<br />\n<br />\n一群等待政府回應訴求的香港人"},{"pid":"21eee70895278edb1e31be2a65ae15d9c9950203","tid":1468502,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:22:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e2025982bb8d095240f027cd6bd48946a3eb480","tid":1468502,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:34:22.000Z","msg":"推"}]}